'''托馬斯·瓊斯·伍德沃德'''爵士，[[OBE|OBE]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/wales/4853732.stm |title=Tom Jones collects his knighthood |publisher=BBC News |date=2006-03-29 |accessdate=2009-03-29 |archive-date=2010-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100403015151/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/wales/4853732.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=KtB>"[http://www.london-gazette.co.uk/issues/57855/supplements/1 (Supplement) no. 57855] {{Wayback|url=http://www.london-gazette.co.uk/issues/57855/supplements/1 |date=20090519234342 }}", ''London Gazette'', 31 December 2005, pp. 1–30.</ref>（Sir '''Thomas Jones Woodward'''，{{bd|1940年|6月7日|迄今|catIdx=Jones, Sir Tom}}），藝名'''湯姆·瓊斯'''（'''Tom Jones'''），2006年封爵後也被坊間尊稱為'''湯·鍾士'''爵士（Sir '''Tom Jones'''），[[英國|英國]][[威爾斯|威爾斯]][[歌手|歌手]]，自1965年出道以來售出超過一億張唱片<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/english/Entertainment/2009-07-06-voa44.cfm |title=Music Icon Tom Jones Remains Sex Symbol After Four Decades |first=Larry |last=London |publisher=[[美國之音|Voice of America]] |date=2009-07-06 |accessdate=2009-08-07 |archive-date=2009-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090806222123/http://www.voanews.com/english/Entertainment/2009-07-06-voa44.cfm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的代表作眾多，包括36首曾經在英國打入{{link-en|40強排行榜|Top 40}}的歌曲，例如：《{{link-en|這並非不尋常|It's Not Unusual}}》（{{lang|en|It's Not Unusual}}）、《{{link-en|風流紳士|What's New Pussycat? (song)}}》（{{lang|en|What's New Pussycat? }}）、《{{link-en|她是一個淑女|She's a Lady}}》（{{lang|en|She's a Lady}}）、《{{link-en|性愛炸彈|Sex Bomb (song)}}》（{{lang|en|Sex Bomb}}）等，首首都是經典名曲<ref>[http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=wBeEDJhw110C&pg=PA28&dq=tom+jones+grammy+award+s.net&hl=en&sa=X&ei=DIWBT7Vf6NTRBdjWgIEH&ved=0CEIQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=tom%20jones%20grammy%20award%20s.net&f=false Howie Richmond Hitmaker Award: Tom Jones] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=wBeEDJhw110C&pg=PA28&dq=tom+jones+grammy+award+s.net&hl=en&sa=X&ei=DIWBT7Vf6NTRBdjWgIEH&ved=0CEIQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=tom%20jones%20grammy%20award%20s.net&f=false |date=20141215023626 }}. p.28. Billboard (20 June 2009). Retrieved 8 April 2012</ref><ref>[https://archive.is/20121216054904/http://www.chartstats.com/artistinfo.php?id=1766 UK Chart Stats: Tom Jones]. Chartstats.com. Retrieved 8 April 2012</ref>。

== 早年生活 ==
他在英國[[南威爾斯|南威爾斯]]小鎮{{link-en|翠佛瑞|Treforest}}（{{lang|en|Treforest}}）出生，父親老托馬斯·伍德沃德是名煤炭[[礦工|礦工]]，母親娘家姓氏為瓊斯。他的祖父母和外祖母都是[[英格蘭人|英格蘭人]]，外祖父為[[威爾士人|威爾士人]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/howaboutthat/5490511/Sir-Tom-Jones-is-English.html |title=Sir Tom Jones 'is English' |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2009-06-10 |publisher=[[Telegraph_Media_Group|TMG]] |location=London |issn=0307-1235 |oclc=49632006 |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2015-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150625234435/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/howaboutthat/5490511/Sir-Tom-Jones-is-English.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他年幼時已經喜愛唱歌，在家庭聚會和婚宴上都會高歌，課餘亦會參加學校的[[合唱團|合唱團]]。他討厭上學，但是在唱歌中找到自信<ref name="DIDiscs TJ">{{cite episode |title=Desert Island Discs with Tom Jones |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00tx499 |series=Desert Island Discs |serieslink=Desert Island Discs |network=[[BBC|BBC]] |station=[[BBC_Radio_4|Radio 4]] |airdate=2010-09-26 |access-date=2015-07-17 |archive-date=2015-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612050747/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00tx499 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12歲那年曾經染上[[肺結核|肺結核]]，需要臥床兩年方能痊癒，期間他可以做的只有聽歌和畫畫<ref>Lucy Ellis & Bryony Sutherland, ''Tom Jones Close Up'', p. 9-10.</ref>。

1957年，與中學同學梅林達·特倫查德（{{lang|en|Melinda Trenchard}}）奉子成婚，二人當時只得16歲<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1298013/Tom-Jones-70-finally-looks-old-53-year-old-son-stops-dyeing-hair.html Tom Jones, 70, finally looks as old as his 53-year-old son as he stops dyeing his hair] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1298013/Tom-Jones-70-finally-looks-old-53-year-old-son-stops-dyeing-hair.html |date=20150713204330 }} – ''Daily Mail''. By Georgina Littlejohn. Published 27 July 2010. Retrieved 12 April 2012.</ref>。為了生計，曾經在手套工廠打工，亦試過從事建築<ref name="Tom Jones NNDB">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nndb.com/people/347/000025272/ |title="Tom Jones NNDB" |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archive-date=2015-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150806044750/http://www.nndb.com/people/347/000025272/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 感情生活 ==
他有過多次越軌的記錄<ref>[http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/2009/02/21/tom-jones-i-still-love-linda-91466-22978645/2/ Tom Jones 'I still love Linda'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/2009/02/21/tom-jones-i-still-love-linda-91466-22978645/2/ |date=20130409233505 }} – WalesOnline.co.uk. Published 21 February 2009. Retrieved 12 April 2012.</ref>，在事業全盛時期，身邊的女伴無數，甚至有說他一年有多達250次[[多人性交|多人性交]]，傳過緋聞的女子包括：[[至上女聲組合|至上女聲組合]]成員{{link-en|瑪麗·威爾遜|Mary Wilson (singer)}}（{{lang|en|Mary Wilson}}）、前世界小姐{{link-en|馬喬裡·華萊士|Marjorie Wallace}}（{{lang|en|Marjorie Wallace}}）、女星{{link-en|卡桑德拉·彼得森|Cassandra Peterson}}（{{lang|en|Cassandra Peterson}}）。他的元配雖然曾經為此沮喪，甚至向湯·鍾斯施襲，但始終對他不離不棄<ref name= "Daily Mail">{{cite news |date=2006-09-13 |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-404951/Tom-Jones-reveals-night-wife-beat-black-blue.html |title=Tom Jones reveals the night my wife beat me black and blue |work=MailOnline |last=Moodie |first=Clemmie |accessdate=2009-07-16 |archive-date=2015-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721015356/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-404951/Tom-Jones-reveals-night-wife-beat-black-blue.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1987年10月，在美國巡迴表演期間曾經跟模特兒凱瑟琳·博克利（{{lang|en|Katherine Berkery}}）有過一段霧水情緣。凱瑟琳為他誕下麟兒，但經過法庭裁決和[[親子鑑定|親子鑑定]]後，他依然不認兒子。

